Jim !

479
00:34:38.583 --> 00:34:39.939
<font color="#ffff33">Tow line's got me! Cut me loose. My leg's broken.</font>
Je suis coincé !

480
00:34:39.959 --> 00:34:42.375
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Coupe la sangle.

481
00:34:44.250 --> 00:34:45.980
<font color="#ffff33">Cut me loose or you're all going in!</font>
Vite. ou vous coulerez !

482
00:34:46.000 --> 00:34:49.980
<font color="#ffff33">The tow line's got me and my leg's broken. Do it.</font>
Je suis coincé et ma jambe est cassée.

483
00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:50.855
<font color="#ffff33">-Do it! -I can't.</font>
Vas-y !

484
00:34:50.875 --> 00:34:52.063
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Je peux pas.

485
00:34:52.083 --> 00:34:54.042
<font color="#ffff33">Do it! Do it!</font>
Vas-y !

486
00:34:58.417 --> 00:35:00.417
<font color="#ffff33">Jesus.</font>
Bon Dieu.

487
00:35:08.542 --> 00:35:10.542
<font color="#ffff33">Holy shit!</font>
Putain de merde !

488
00:35:14.459 --> 00:35:16.458
<font color="#ffff33">It's spreading out.</font>
Ça s'étend.

489
00:35:16.500 --> 00:35:18.272
<font color="#ffff33">Meaning what?</font>
Ça veut dire quoi ?

490
00:35:18.292 --> 00:35:22.772
<font color="#ffff33">Meaning it's going to keep cracking for two. maybe three thousand meters.</font>
Que les fissures vont se propager sur 2000 ou 3000 m.

491
00:35:22.792 --> 00:35:24.230
<font color="#ffff33">That's over a mile.</font>
C'est énorme.

492
00:35:24.250 --> 00:35:25.980
<font color="#ffff33">We'll outrun it. Let's move!</font>
Il faut foncer. En route !

493
00:35:26.000 --> 00:35:27.688
<font color="#ffff33">We got to unhook first.</font>
On doit enlever le câble.

494
00:35:27.708 --> 00:35:29.750
<font color="#ffff33">There's no time.</font>
Pas le temps.

495
00:35:29.917 --> 00:35:34.084
<font color="#ffff33">We're going to have to run tied together. Go!</font>
On devra rouler attachés. On y va !

496
00:35:40.042 --> 00:35:42.125
<font color="#ffff33">Get your harness on.</font>
Mettez le harnais.

497
00:36:00.459 --> 00:36:03.272
<font color="#ffff33">Mike. come in. We got to hike up the speed. Over.</font>
Mike. on doit accélérer. A toi.

498
00:36:03.292 --> 00:36:04.959
<font color="#ffff33">Roger.</font>
Reçu.

499
00:36:28.542 --> 00:36:31.189
<font color="#ffff33">Mike. come in. We got to run faster. Roger. Gurty. running board.</font>
- On doit aller plus vite. - Reçu.

500
00:36:31.209 --> 00:36:33.417
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Gurty. Marchepied.

501
00:36:38.834 --> 00:36:41.355
<font color="#ffff33">-Get out. On the running board. -Why? So if we go through. we can jump clear.</font>
- Allez sur le marchepied. - Pourquoi ?

502
00:36:41.375 --> 00:36:43.375
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Pour pouvoir sauter.

503
00:37:02.625 --> 00:37:05.438
<font color="#ffff33">Got a pressure wave ahead of me.</font>
Onde de pression devant !

504
00:37:05.458 --> 00:37:11.209
<font color="#ffff33">Well. I got one hell of an ice crack behind me here. so how do you want to die?</font>
Ça s'effondre derrière moi. Tu préfères mourir comment ?

505
00:37:16.500 --> 00:37:21.292
<font color="#ffff33">Slush bed at 200 yards. Get in and buckle up.</font>
Congère à 200 m ! Remontez et attachez-vous.

506
00:37:22.917 --> 00:37:26.834
<font color="#ffff33">Hang on. pal. This is going to get ugly.</font>
Accroche-toi. Ça va secouer.

507
00:37:31.834 --> 00:37:33.105
<font color="#ffff33">This is not good.</font>
C'est pas bon.

508
00:37:33.125 --> 00:37:36.209
<font color="#ffff33">This is not good. This is not good!</font>
pas bon du tout !

509
00:37:42.459 --> 00:37:44.417
<font color="#ffff33">I don't like this!</font>
J'aime pas ça !

510
00:37:48.125 --> 00:37:49.834
<font color="#ffff33">Shit!</font>
Merde !

511
00:38:05.625 --> 00:38:07.272
<font color="#ffff33">I've got your seat belt.</font>
Coupe ta ceinture.

512
00:38:07.292 --> 00:38:09.709
<font color="#ffff33">You okay. pal?</font>
Ça va. mon grand ?

513
00:38:25.042 --> 00:38:26.959
<font color="#ffff33">We're finished.</font>
On est foutus.

514
00:38:37.042 --> 00:38:39.250
<font color="#ffff33">It stopped.</font>
Ça s'est arrêté.

515
00:38:42.583 --> 00:38:44.147
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah.</font>


516
00:38:44.167 --> 00:38:45.689
<font color="#ffff33">It stopped!</font>
Ça s'est arrêté !

517
00:38:45.709 --> 00:38:47.563
<font color="#ffff33">We capsized for a reason.</font>
Il fallait qu'on se renverse.

518
00:38:47.583 --> 00:38:53.334
<font color="#ffff33">Now our weight's displaced evenly instead of on the tires.</font>
Notre poids s'est réparti et ne porte plus uniquement sur les roues.

519
00:38:54.625 --> 00:38:57.189
<font color="#ffff33">So based on seven liters per minute. per man...</font>
Disons 7 litres par minute et par homme.

520
00:38:57.209 --> 00:38:59.022
<font color="#ffff33">Seven liters?</font>
7 litres ?

521
00:38:59.042 --> 00:39:00.855
<font color="#ffff33">That's all a grown man breathes?</font>
Un adulte n'inspire que ça ?

522
00:39:00.875 --> 00:39:04.480
<font color="#ffff33">When at rest. the figure doubles with physical exertion.</font>
Au repos. Ça double lors d'un effort.

523
00:39:04.500 --> 00:39:06.064
<font color="#ffff33">Hey. Cody. can I ask you something?</font>
Cody.

524
00:39:06.084 --> 00:39:07.855
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Je peux te poser une question ?

525
00:39:07.875 --> 00:39:10.355
<font color="#ffff33">-Sure. -When the mine blew up.</font>
Vas-y.

526
00:39:10.375 --> 00:39:12.480
<font color="#ffff33">I said we hit a methane pocket</font>
Au moment de l'explosion. j'ai pensé à une poche de méthane

527
00:39:12.500 --> 00:39:14.772
<font color="#ffff33">and you said "That's impossible."</font>
et tu as dit : "C'est impossible."

528
00:39:14.792 --> 00:39:16.792
<font color="#ffff33">Why?</font>
Pourquoi ?

529
00:39:20.625 --> 00:39:22.834
<font color="#ffff33">It's still settling.</font>
Ça secoue encore.

530
00:39:39.792 --> 00:39:42.334
<font color="#ffff33">Air compressor.</font>
"Compresseur d'air".

531
00:39:42.917 --> 00:39:46.500
<font color="#ffff33">Thank God. they're coming through.</font>
C'est bon. ils arrivent.

532
00:39:49.667 --> 00:39:51.750
<font color="#ffff33">Failed.</font>
"Echec".

533
00:39:55.750 --> 00:39:57.458
<font color="#ffff33">Hey. what's the story. Cody?</font>
Du nouveau. Cody ?

534
00:39:59.625 --> 00:40:01.792
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. What'd they say?</font>
Ils disent quoi ?

535
00:40:08.917 --> 00:40:12.834
<font color="#ffff33">They say they're still working on it.</font>
Ils cherchent une solution.

536
00:40:15.584 --> 00:40:18.334
<font color="#ffff33">- Cody. - Yeah?</font>
Cody.

537
00:40:23.709 --> 00:40:25.564
<font color="#ffff33">You didn't answer my question.</font>
Tu ne m'as pas répondu.

538
00:40:25.584 --> 00:40:30.000
<font color="#ffff33">Why is it impossible we hit a methane pocket?</font>
Pourquoi ça ne peut pas être une poche de méthane ?

539
00:40:33.209 --> 00:40:35.563
<font color="#ffff33">Because I was told it would never happen.</font>
Ils ont dit que ça n'arriverait pas.

540
00:40:35.583 --> 00:40:37.022
<font color="#ffff33">By who?</font>
Qui ?

541
00:40:37.042 --> 00:40:39.209
<font color="#ffff33">Who told you that?</font>
Qui t'a dit ça ?

542
00:40:40.958 --> 00:40:43.500
<font color="#ffff33">Cody.</font>


543
00:40:47.542 --> 00:40:49.938
<font color="#ffff33">Easy. boys! Easy! Get him out!</font>
Doucement. les gars. Dégagez-les !

544
00:40:49.958 --> 00:40:51.959
<font color="#ffff33">Easy!</font>
Doucement !

545
00:40:56.750 --> 00:40:58.667
<font color="#ffff33">Cody!</font>
Cody !

546
00:41:00.667 --> 00:41:04.583
<font color="#ffff33">Whoa! Whoa!</font>


547
00:41:23.792 --> 00:41:25.813
<font color="#ffff33">SOS. SOS.</font>
SOS. SOS.

548
00:41:25.833 --> 00:41:27.647
<font color="#ffff33">41 .40.</font>
41.4-0.

549
00:41:27.667 --> 00:41:29.730
<font color="#ffff33">Ice road north of 53.</font>
Route de glace au nord de la 53.

550
00:41:29.750 --> 00:41:31.522
<font color="#ffff33">Kenworth through the ice.</font>
Un camion a sombré.

551
00:41:31.542 --> 00:41:33.980
<font color="#ffff33">Repeat: Kenworth through the ice.</font>
Je répète : un camion a sombré.

552
00:41:34.000 --> 00:41:35.855
<font color="#ffff33">Copy. Are there survivors?</font>
Reçu. Des survivants ?

553
00:41:35.875 --> 00:41:37.772
<font color="#ffff33">Negative.</font>
Négatif.

554
00:41:37.792 --> 00:41:41.105
<font color="#ffff33">We are responding. thank you.</font>
On s'en occupe. Merci.

555
00:41:41.125 --> 00:41:42.605
<font color="#ffff33">Wait. wait. wait. wait. What about us?</font>
Minute.

556
00:41:42.625 --> 00:41:43.772
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Et nous ?

557
00:41:43.792 --> 00:41:46.084
<font color="#ffff33">What about us?</font>
Nous. quoi ?

558
00:41:49.334 --> 00:41:52.125
<font color="#ffff33">We're heading back. right?</font>
On fait demi-tour. non ?

559
00:41:52.875 --> 00:41:54.938
<font color="#ffff33">-Back? -Yeah.</font>
Demi-tour ?

560
00:41:54.958 --> 00:41:56.938
<font color="#ffff33">That's what I said.</font>
Oui. C'est ce que j'ai dit.

561
00:41:56.958 --> 00:41:59.730
<font color="#ffff33">The ice is bound to be thinner to the south. not thicker.</font>
La glace va fondre au sud. pas épaissir.

562
00:41:59.750 --> 00:42:03.230
<font color="#ffff33">We still have two deliverable wellheads. Tactical redundancy. remember?</font>
Il nous reste deux têtes de puits. Redondance tactique.

563
00:42:03.250 --> 00:42:05.522
<font color="#ffff33">And we're more than halfway there.</font>
On a fait la moitié du chemin.

564
00:42:05.542 --> 00:42:07.542
<font color="#ffff33">What do you think. Gurty?</font>
Qu'en dis-tu. Gurty ?

565
00:42:08.875 --> 00:42:11.480
<font color="#ffff33">Attaboy. Are you coming with. Tantoo?</font>
C'est bien. Tu en es. Tantoo ?

566
00:42:11.500 --> 00:42:13.397
<font color="#ffff33">-Hell. yeah. -What? This is ridiculous.</font>
Grave.

567
00:42:13.417 --> 00:42:15.313
<font color="#ffff33">You're all going to die.</font>
C'est ridicule. Vous allez tous mourir.

568
00:42:15.333 --> 00:42:21.375
<font color="#ffff33">You want to go back. go back. I suggest you do it quick.</font>
Faites demi-tour si vous voulez. Mais ne traînez pas.

569
00:42:21.500 --> 00:42:23.022
<font color="#ffff33">Nichiiwad.</font>
Un nichiiwad.

570
00:42:23.042 --> 00:42:24.355
<font color="#ffff33">The big one.</font>
Il est énorme.

571
00:42:24.375 --> 00:42:26.272
<font color="#ffff33">Drop 50 degrees. we'll pick up 8 to 10 centimeters of new ice.</font>
On va perdre 10 degrés.

572
00:42:26.292 --> 00:42:29.480
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Il va y avoir 8 à 10 cm de glace fraîche.

573
00:42:29.500 --> 00:42:31.897
<font color="#ffff33">Let's get the rigs upright and haul ass.</font>
On redresse les camions et on fonce.

574
00:42:31.917 --> 00:42:33.355
<font color="#ffff33">We're back in business.</font>
C'est reparti !

575
00:42:33.375 --> 00:42:36.022
<font color="#ffff33">You're out of your minds. All of you!</font>
Vous êtes dingues. tous les trois.

576
00:42:36.042 --> 00:42:38.084
<font color="#ffff33">Wait. wait. wait.</font>
Attendez.

577
00:42:38.375 --> 00:42:40.438
<font color="#ffff33">It appears you're the new leader here. so--</font>
C'est vous qui dirigez maintenant...

578
00:42:40.458 --> 00:42:41.814
<font color="#ffff33">I'm not the leader of anything.</font>
Je ne dirige rien du tout.

579
00:42:41.834 --> 00:42:43.855
<font color="#ffff33">Everyone's on their own.</font>
C'est chacun pour soi.

580
00:42:43.875 --> 00:42:46.584
<font color="#ffff33">Fine. Whatever.</font>
D'accord. Peu importe.

581
00:42:47.750 --> 00:42:51.272
<font color="#ffff33">You're not curious about back there. what happened?</font>
Ce qui s'est passé ne vous paraît pas étrange ?

582
00:42:51.292 --> 00:42:52.397
<font color="#ffff33">We saw what happened.</font>
On a vu l'accident.

583
00:42:52.417 --> 00:42:56.875
<font color="#ffff33">No. I'm talking about the seized-up engine.</font>
Je parle du moteur qui s'est grippé.

584
00:42:58.000 --> 00:43:00.000
<font color="#ffff33">Go on.</font>
Continuez.

585
00:43:01.417 --> 00:43:04.105
<font color="#ffff33">How well do you know her? Tantoo?</font>
Qu'est-ce que vous savez de Tantoo ?

586
00:43:04.125 --> 00:43:08.625
<font color="#ffff33">Met her first time yesterday. Why?</font>
Je ne la connais que depuis hier. Pourquoi ?

587
00:43:10.917 --> 00:43:14.167
<font color="#ffff33">Mind answering a couple of questions?</font>
On peut te parler ?

588
00:43:14.459 --> 00:43:17.897
<font color="#ffff33">You worked for Jim Goldenrod. what. two years?</font>
Tu as bossé pour Jim Goldenrod deux ans ?

589
00:43:17.917 --> 00:43:20.125
<font color="#ffff33">Two and a half.</font>
Deux ans et demi.

590
00:43:20.875 --> 00:43:23.000
<font color="#ffff33">Why'd it end?</font>
Pourquoi ça s'est fini ?

591
00:43:23.917 --> 00:43:27.397
<font color="#ffff33">I used his rig on the weekend without permission.</font>
J'ai pris son camion un week-end sans demander.

592
00:43:27.417 --> 00:43:30.772
<font color="#ffff33">So you're a thief. I'm not a thief.</font>
- Donc tu es une voleuse. - Non.

593
00:43:30.792 --> 00:43:34.750
<font color="#ffff33">Hey. I was hauling banners for a demon--</font>
J'en avais besoin pour une manif...

594
00:43:35.209 --> 00:43:36.689
<font color="#ffff33">What is this your business?</font>
En quoi ça vous regarde ?

595
00:43:36.709 --> 00:43:40.689
<font color="#ffff33">You weren't a happy camper. were you? When he fired you?</font>
Tu n'as pas vraiment apprécié qu'il te vire.

596
00:43:40.709 --> 00:43:42.542
<font color="#ffff33">No. I... Look. just--</font>
Non.

597
00:43:44.209 --> 00:43:47.855
<font color="#ffff33">I've never seen a Kenworth with less than 10k on the odometer</font>
Je n'ai jamais vu un Kenworth avec moins de 10 000 km au compteur

598
00:43:47.875 --> 00:43:50.272
<font color="#ffff33">-just up and quit. have you? -No.</font>
tomber en rade. Et toi ?

599
00:43:50.292 --> 00:43:51.480
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Non.

600
00:43:51.500 --> 00:43:54.147
<font color="#ffff33">Most diesel engines don't seize on their own.</font>
Un diesel ne se grippe pas comme ça.

601
00:43:54.167 --> 00:43:56.625
<font color="#ffff33">Unless they burn gasoline.</font>
Sauf s'il pompe de l'essence.

602
00:43:57.750 --> 00:43:59.063
<font color="#ffff33">What's this about?</font>
C'est quoi. ce délire ?

603
00:43:59.083 --> 00:44:02.105
<font color="#ffff33">You dosed Goldenrod's rig with gas while we were loading up.</font>
Tu as mis de l'essence

604
00:44:02.125 --> 00:44:03.709
<font color="#ffff33">I saw you next to the pump.</font>
dans son camion avant le départ.

605
00:44:03.792 --> 00:44:05.814
<font color="#ffff33">You said you were checking the tire pressure.</font>
Tu étais près des pompes. soi-disant pour vérifier les pneus.

606
00:44:05.834 --> 00:44:07.772
<font color="#ffff33">That is a goddamn lie.</font>
C'est des conneries.

607
00:44:07.792 --> 00:44:12.147
<font color="#ffff33">You were going to take us all out. weren't you? So you could claim the whole 200 grand.</font>
Tu comptais tous nous éliminer. pour toucher la totalité de la prime.

608
00:44:12.167 --> 00:44:13.772
<font color="#ffff33">No. I don't know what you're talking about.</font>
C'est n'importe quoi !

609
00:44:13.792 --> 00:44:17.313
<font color="#ffff33">Who else. then? It wasn't me. Wasn't Gurty. Wasn't him.</font>
Ça ne peut être que toi. Pas moi. ni Gurty. ni lui.

610
00:44:17.333 --> 00:44:21.772
<font color="#ffff33">He works for the company that's paying us. This is not about the money for me. you idiots!</font>
Il bosse pour la boîte qui nous paye.

611
00:44:21.792 --> 00:44:22.147
<font color="#ffff33">God. my brother is in that mine.</font>
Je fais pas ça pour le fric. crétins.

612
00:44:22.167 --> 00:44:23.688
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Mon frère est dans la mine.

613
00:44:23.708 --> 00:44:26.147
<font color="#ffff33">And the longer that we stand here. the closer he is to dying.</font>
Si on reste plantés là.

614
00:44:26.167 --> 00:44:28.563
<font color="#ffff33">-so if you could just move-- -She's lying.</font>
il mourra. alors poussez-vous.

615
00:44:28.583 --> 00:44:30.897
<font color="#ffff33">You can't trust these people.</font>
Elle ment. Ces gens-là sont fourbes.

616
00:44:30.917 --> 00:44:33.355
<font color="#ffff33">Call Katka. His name is Cody Mantooth.</font>
Appelle Katka. Il s'appelle Cody Mantooth.

617
00:44:33.375 --> 00:44:35.563
<font color="#ffff33">We have different fathers.</font>
On n'a pas le même père.

618
00:44:35.583 --> 00:44:38.125
<font color="#ffff33">God. "these people"? You're a racist asshole...</font>
Ces gens-là ?

619
00:44:38.708 --> 00:44:39.105
<font color="#ffff33">-You're not going anywhere. -Look. just get out--</font>
Sale connard raciste.

620
00:44:39.125 --> 00:44:40.022
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Tu restes ici.

621
00:44:40.042 --> 00:44:41.105
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Laissez-moi.

622
00:44:41.125 --> 00:44:42.980
<font color="#ffff33">-You're not going anywhere. -Fine.</font>
Tu restes ici.

623
00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:45.167
<font color="#ffff33">Hey. hey. hey. Whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa.</font>
D'accord.

624
00:44:54.959 --> 00:44:56.897
<font color="#ffff33">We call the company and check your story.</font>
On va vérifier ton histoire.

625
00:44:56.917 --> 00:44:59.272
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. and then go fuck yourself.</font>
Vous l'aurez bien profond.

626
00:44:59.292 --> 00:45:01.542
<font color="#ffff33">Tie her up. Gurty.</font>
Attache-la. Gurty.

627
00:45:53.417 --> 00:45:54.897
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. Tully. it's Mike.</font>
Tully. c'est Mike.

628
00:45:54.917 --> 00:45:58.230
<font color="#ffff33">I just heard about Goldenrod from County Emergency. what happened?</font>
On m'a prévenu pour Goldenrod. Que s'est-il passé ?

629
00:45:58.250 --> 00:46:01.188
<font color="#ffff33">We think Tantoo dosed Jim's rig with gasoline.</font>
On pense que Tantoo a mis de l'essence dans son réservoir.

630
00:46:01.208 --> 00:46:03.688
<font color="#ffff33">Are you kidding? That's worse than putting sugar in the tank.</font>
Sérieux ? C'est pire que de mettre du sucre.

631
00:46:03.708 --> 00:46:06.897
<font color="#ffff33">Contact Katka. ask them if there's a miner.</font>
Appelez Katka.

632
00:46:06.917 --> 00:46:09.605
<font color="#ffff33">Cody Mantooth. on the missing list.</font>
Demandez si un certain Cody Mantooth fait partie des disparus.

633
00:46:09.625 --> 00:46:13.500
<font color="#ffff33">-I'll explain later. -You got it.</font>
- Je vous expliquerai. - Ça marche.

634
00:46:24.500 --> 00:46:25.772
<font color="#ffff33">-We want to discuss options. -Like what?</font>
On a une proposition.

635
00:46:25.792 --> 00:46:27.667
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Laquelle ?

636
00:46:27.792 --> 00:46:31.230
<font color="#ffff33">Like decreasing our numbers.</font>
Réduire notre nombre.

637
00:46:31.250 --> 00:46:34.105
<font color="#ffff33">I want to talk to the folks upstairs. I want to talk to the bosses.</font>
