<font color="#ffff33">How about the driver?</font>
Et la fille ?

805
01:03:10.292 --> 01:03:13.125
<font color="#ffff33">Well. she's alive. sir.</font>
Elle est en vie. monsieur.

806
01:03:17.584 --> 01:03:21.480
<font color="#ffff33">Put the cab through that guardrail up there.</font>
Son camion va quitter la route là-haut.

807
01:03:21.500 --> 01:03:22.647
<font color="#ffff33">Your story is she lost control.</font>
Vous direz

808
01:03:22.667 --> 01:03:24.730
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
qu'elle a perdu le contrôle

809
01:03:24.750 --> 01:03:28.772
<font color="#ffff33">you dove for safety before it went over. -You clear? -Clear. sir.</font>
et que vous avez sauté in extremis. Compris ?

810
01:03:28.792 --> 01:03:30.272
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Compris.

811
01:03:30.292 --> 01:03:33.063
<font color="#ffff33">The miners' oxygen window closes in three hours.</font>
L'oxygène des mineurs

812
01:03:33.083 --> 01:03:36.105
<font color="#ffff33">so the press is going to be all over us.</font>
sera épuisé dans 3 heures. Nous serons assaillis par la presse.

813
01:03:36.125 --> 01:03:38.855
<font color="#ffff33">They need to be told our valiant rescue had a tragic end.</font>
Nous devrons déclarer que notre convoi héroïque

814
01:03:38.875 --> 01:03:40.689
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
a connu une fin tragique.

815
01:03:40.709 --> 01:03:42.397
<font color="#ffff33">I'll make it happen. sir.</font>
Je m'en occupe. monsieur.

816
01:03:42.417 --> 01:03:44.542
<font color="#ffff33">Good. Good.</font>
Bien.

817
01:03:44.917 --> 01:03:48.209
<font color="#ffff33">You call me when it's done.</font>
J'attendrai votre appel.

818
01:04:10.584 --> 01:04:12.772
<font color="#ffff33">If you do this. it's on your head.</font>
Vous devrez répondre de vos actes.

819
01:04:12.792 --> 01:04:14.563
<font color="#ffff33">You want to blame someone. blame management.</font>
Va dire ça à nos dirigeants.

820
01:04:14.583 --> 01:04:17.564
<font color="#ffff33">What has management got to do with it?</font>
Quel rapport avec eux ?

821
01:04:17.584 --> 01:04:20.980
<font color="#ffff33">All those in favor. raise your-- Mankins!</font>
- Ceux qui sont pour... - Mankins !

822
01:04:21.000 --> 01:04:22.188
<font color="#ffff33">I asked you a question.</font>
Réponds.

823
01:04:22.208 --> 01:04:25.814
<font color="#ffff33">Because they made us cut the damn sensors. René.</font>
Ils nous ont fait couper les détecteurs.

824
01:04:25.834 --> 01:04:27.292
<font color="#ffff33">They what?</font>
Quoi ?

825
01:04:27.792 --> 01:04:30.855
<font color="#ffff33">They claimed the new quotas were killing them.</font>
S'ils veulent tenir les quotas.

826
01:04:30.875 --> 01:04:32.939
<font color="#ffff33">so they couldn't afford a shutdown.</font>
ils peuvent pas fermer.

827
01:04:32.959 --> 01:04:35.605
<font color="#ffff33">They said there was no chance of gas pockets this far north.</font>
Selon eux. il pouvait pas y avoir

828
01:04:35.625 --> 01:04:37.939
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
de poche de gaz par ici.

829
01:04:37.959 --> 01:04:39.772
<font color="#ffff33">And they sweetened the deal.</font>
On a eu une carotte.

830
01:04:39.792 --> 01:04:41.792
<font color="#ffff33">How much?</font>
Combien ?

831
01:04:46.375 --> 01:04:50.459
<font color="#ffff33">Hundred dollars per man per month.</font>
100 $ par tête et par mois.

832
01:04:50.917 --> 01:04:54.313
<font color="#ffff33">You turned off the gas sensors for $100 a month?</font>
Vous avez coupé les détecteurs pour 100 $ par mois ?

833
01:04:54.333 --> 01:04:56.772
<font color="#ffff33">And anyone who blew the whistle gets shit-canned.</font>
Si on l'ouvrait. on était viré.

834
01:04:56.792 --> 01:04:58.397
<font color="#ffff33">None of that matters now. René.</font>
Ça n'a plus d'importance.

835
01:04:58.417 --> 01:05:00.689
<font color="#ffff33">Our oxygen is falling fast.</font>
On va manquer d'oxygène.

836
01:05:00.709 --> 01:05:02.147
<font color="#ffff33">There's a vote on the floor.</font>
On doit voter.

837
01:05:02.167 --> 01:05:03.938
<font color="#ffff33">All those in favor. raise your hands.</font>
Pour : levez la main.

838
01:05:03.958 --> 01:05:06.333
<font color="#ffff33">No.</font>


839
01:05:07.750 --> 01:05:10.355
<font color="#ffff33">Hey!</font>


840
01:05:10.375 --> 01:05:12.397
<font color="#ffff33">How much methane do you think is in here now?</font>
Combien de méthane il y a ici ?

841
01:05:12.417 --> 01:05:14.439
<font color="#ffff33">Huh?</font>


842
01:05:14.459 --> 01:05:16.730
<font color="#ffff33">These men are not the enemy.</font>
Ce n'est pas eux l'ennemi.

843
01:05:16.750 --> 01:05:19.105
<font color="#ffff33">The enemy's up there. Bullshit!</font>
- L'ennemi est là-haut. - Des clous !

844
01:05:19.125 --> 01:05:21.022
<font color="#ffff33">The enemy's asphyxiation.</font>
L'ennemi. c'est l'asphyxie.

845
01:05:21.042 --> 01:05:23.355
<font color="#ffff33">We're getting out of here together.</font>
On sortira d'ici ensemble

846
01:05:23.375 --> 01:05:24.939
<font color="#ffff33">or not at all.</font>
ou pas du tout.

847
01:05:24.959 --> 01:05:29.375
<font color="#ffff33">You're one stupid son of a bitch. René.</font>
Tu es un putain d'abruti. René.

848
01:05:30.000 --> 01:05:32.272
<font color="#ffff33">You too. Cody.</font>
Toi aussi. Cody.

849
01:05:32.292 --> 01:05:34.355
<font color="#ffff33">Maybe so. but this is how it's going to be.</font>
C'est possible.

850
01:05:34.375 --> 01:05:37.167
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
mais c'est nous qui décidons.

851
01:06:04.375 --> 01:06:06.334
<font color="#ffff33">Right here.</font>
Ici.

852
01:06:07.375 --> 01:06:09.334
<font color="#ffff33">Let's clear the road.</font>
Dégagez la route.

853
01:06:40.750 --> 01:06:42.230
<font color="#ffff33">Ow!</font>


854
01:06:42.250 --> 01:06:44.314
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. that's what I thought.</font>
Je m'en doutais.

855
01:06:44.334 --> 01:06:47.689
<font color="#ffff33">You're never gonna get away with this. There's gonna be an investigation.</font>
Vous vous en tirerez pas. Il y aura une enquête.

856
01:06:47.709 --> 01:06:50.209
<font color="#ffff33">That's the plan.</font>
C'est prévu.

857
01:06:58.000 --> 01:06:59.875
<font color="#ffff33">What is that?</font>
C'est quoi ?

858
01:07:13.917 --> 01:07:16.292
<font color="#ffff33">Ah!</font>


859
01:07:50.167 --> 01:07:51.792
<font color="#ffff33">Thanks.</font>
Merci.

860
01:08:21.209 --> 01:08:23.209
<font color="#ffff33">Mayday! Mayday!</font>
SOS !

861
01:08:23.250 --> 01:08:24.814
<font color="#ffff33">Mayday! Come in! Anybody. come in! Mayday! Mayday!</font>
Répondez. quelqu'un !

862
01:08:24.834 --> 01:08:26.272
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
SOS !

863
01:08:26.292 --> 01:08:28.439
<font color="#ffff33">Mayday! Is anybody out there?</font>
Quelqu'un m'entend ?

864
01:08:28.459 --> 01:08:30.647
<font color="#ffff33">Tantoo. it's Mike.</font>
Tantoo. c'est Mike.

865
01:08:30.667 --> 01:08:34.355
<font color="#ffff33">We're coming up the Pass. -Where are you? -Approaching the upper traverse.</font>
On approche du col. Où es-tu ?

866
01:08:34.375 --> 01:08:36.980
<font color="#ffff33">I got Varnay behind me with others. They're all armed.</font>
Sur la crête. Varnay me poursuit avec des types armés.

867
01:08:37.000 --> 01:08:40.022
<font color="#ffff33">We've got two hours to get to Katka. I'm still pulling weight.</font>
Il reste 2 heures de route et je traîne ma remorque.

868
01:08:40.042 --> 01:08:41.314
<font color="#ffff33">-They're trying to stop us. -Yeah. we figured.</font>
Ils sont après nous.

869
01:08:41.334 --> 01:08:42.980
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Oui. on l'a compris.

870
01:08:43.000 --> 01:08:47.147
<font color="#ffff33">Cody always said that they cut corners with the methane regs. Those bastards. they caused the cave-in.</font>
Cody disait qu'ils contournaient la réglementation.

871
01:08:47.167 --> 01:08:48.897
<font color="#ffff33">now they're trying to cover it up.</font>
L'accident. c'est leur faute et ils veulent le cacher.

872
01:08:48.917 --> 01:08:50.147
<font color="#ffff33">Not going to happen.</font>
Ça n'arrivera pas.

873
01:08:50.167 --> 01:08:53.084
<font color="#ffff33">Just hang on. We're coming.</font>
Tiens bon. On arrive.

874
01:09:05.459 --> 01:09:08.605
<font color="#ffff33">Take them out so it will pass forensics.</font>
Eliminez-les sans laisser d'indices.

875
01:09:08.625 --> 01:09:15.250
<font color="#ffff33">No bullet holes. Do not discharge your weapons.</font>
Pas d'impacts de balles. N'utilisez pas vos armes.

876
01:10:12.292 --> 01:10:14.875
<font color="#ffff33">What?</font>


877
01:10:20.250 --> 01:10:21.564
<font color="#ffff33">Shit.</font>
Merde.

878
01:10:21.584 --> 01:10:26.939
<font color="#ffff33">Oh. come on. One more mile. We can do one more mile. Come on.</font>
Encore 1.5 km. On va y arriver.

879
01:10:26.959 --> 01:10:28.439
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. we can do it. Come on.</font>
On va y arriver.

880
01:10:28.459 --> 01:10:30.334
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Allez.

881
01:10:47.042 --> 01:10:48.834
<font color="#ffff33">Pull over!</font>
Arrêtez-vous !

882
01:10:50.167 --> 01:10:52.064
<font color="#ffff33">Pull over now!</font>
Arrêtez-vous tout de suite.

883
01:10:52.084 --> 01:10:53.939
<font color="#ffff33">Pull over!</font>
Arrêtez-vous !

884
01:10:53.959 --> 01:10:55.772
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Dernier avertissement !

885
01:10:55.792 --> 01:10:59.022
<font color="#ffff33">If they were going to shoot us. they would've done it by now.</font>
S'ils voulaient tirer. ce serait déjà fait.

886
01:10:59.042 --> 01:11:00.814
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. Good. Come on.</font>
C'est ça.

887
01:11:00.834 --> 01:11:02.875
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Obéissez.

888
01:11:03.250 --> 01:11:05.334
<font color="#ffff33">Ready. bro?</font>
Prêt. frérot ?

889
01:11:06.584 --> 01:11:08.959
<font color="#ffff33">Pull over now!</font>
Arrêtez-vous !

890
01:14:19.917 --> 01:14:24.292
<font color="#ffff33">Well. don't just stand there. Let's go.</font>
Ne reste pas planté là. En route.

891
01:14:40.584 --> 01:14:47.417
<font color="#ffff33">Come on. come on. don't stop. don't stop. Don't you dare stop. Come on.</font>
Allez. bon sang. Je t'interdis de t'arrêter.

892
01:14:49.709 --> 01:14:53.167
<font color="#ffff33">Don't do this to me. Don't... Don't do this.</font>
Ne me fais pas ça.

893
01:14:53.709 --> 01:14:57.189
<font color="#ffff33">Come on. keep going. Don't stop. don't stop! Come on. you piece of shit. Let's go.</font>
Ne t'arrête pas ! Avance. gros tas de merde !

894
01:14:57.209 --> 01:15:01.250
<font color="#ffff33">I'm sorry. I didn't mean it. I didn't mean it!</font>
Excuse-moi. Je le pensais pas !

895
01:15:24.875 --> 01:15:28.750
<font color="#ffff33">Don't think that I'm not going to use this on you!</font>
J'hésiterai pas à tirer sur vous !

896
01:15:32.334 --> 01:15:34.375
<font color="#ffff33">What's your game?</font>
A quoi vous jouez ?

897
01:15:35.417 --> 01:15:39.355
<font color="#ffff33">Oh. what. are you just going to stand there?</font>
Vous allez rester là-bas ?

898
01:15:39.375 --> 01:15:40.980
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah.</font>
Oui.

899
01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:44.147
<font color="#ffff33">This is the last wellhead. What are you going to do?</font>
C'est la dernière tête de puits. Tu vas faire quoi ?

900
01:15:44.167 --> 01:15:46.730
<font color="#ffff33">You going to push it the rest of the way? Because if you're going to make it to Katka</font>
La pousser sur le reste du trajet ?

901
01:15:46.750 --> 01:15:48.647
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
Si tu veux être à la mine

902
01:15:48.667 --> 01:15:52.022
<font color="#ffff33">before your brother stops breathing.</font>
avant que ton frère cesse de respirer.

903
01:15:52.042 --> 01:15:55.750
<font color="#ffff33">that's what you're going to have to do.</font>
c'est la seule solution.

904
01:15:59.042 --> 01:16:01.814
<font color="#ffff33">The other drivers are going to come.</font>
Les autres chauffeurs vont arriver.

905
01:16:01.834 --> 01:16:04.417
<font color="#ffff33">The other drivers are dead.</font>
Ils sont morts !

906
01:16:46.875 --> 01:16:49.314
<font color="#ffff33">He ripped out my fuel equalizer.</font>
Il a arraché ma durite d'essence.

907
01:16:49.334 --> 01:16:51.583
<font color="#ffff33">Gurty can fix that.</font>
Gurty va réparer ça.

908
01:16:52.250 --> 01:16:58.689
<font color="#ffff33">We'll change out your fuel line and siphon enough juice to get you down to Katka.</font>
On va siphonner notre réservoir pour que tu aies de quoi aller à Katka.

909
01:16:58.709 --> 01:17:00.480
<font color="#ffff33">Listen...</font>
Ecoute.

910
01:17:00.500 --> 01:17:02.522
<font color="#ffff33">we...</font>


911
01:17:02.542 --> 01:17:05.167
<font color="#ffff33">we seriously misjudged you.</font>
On s'est trompés à ton sujet.

912
01:17:05.375 --> 01:17:07.375
<font color="#ffff33">Friends?</font>
Amis ?

913
01:17:09.709 --> 01:17:11.334
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah.</font>
Oui.

914
01:18:21.459 --> 01:18:23.397
<font color="#ffff33">Hey. how long do you think all this is going to take?</font>
Ça va prendre longtemps ?

915
01:18:23.417 --> 01:18:27.188
<font color="#ffff33">A couple of minutes. I know you're anxious -about your brother. -Yeah.</font>
Quelques minutes. Je sais que tu penses à ton frère.

916
01:18:27.208 --> 01:18:30.480
<font color="#ffff33">Cody's all I got. you know? It's kind of like you and yours.</font>
J'ai que lui dans la vie. Tu connais ça.

917
01:18:30.500 --> 01:18:32.417
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah.</font>


918
01:18:34.292 --> 01:18:36.689
<font color="#ffff33">Gurty's like that commercial.</font>
Gurty est comme dans la pub :

919
01:18:36.709 --> 01:18:41.084
<font color="#ffff33">Takes a lickin' but keeps on tickin'.</font>
"Quand y en a plus. y en a encore."

920
01:19:33.250 --> 01:19:35.792
<font color="#ffff33">That last can should do it.</font>
Après ce bidon. ça suffira.

921
01:19:36.042 --> 01:19:40.542
<font color="#ffff33">He saved my life. Give him a treat.</font>
Il m'a sauvé la vie. Offre-lui un festin.

922
01:19:50.750 --> 01:19:54.355
<font color="#ffff33">We can't stay here and we can't back up.</font>
On ne peut pas rester là. ni reculer.

923
01:19:54.375 --> 01:19:55.438
<font color="#ffff33">We'll have to outrun it.</font>
On doit foncer.

924
01:19:55.458 --> 01:19:59.750
<font color="#ffff33">-You're dreaming. -You got a better idea?</font>
- Tu rêves. - Tu as une meilleure idée ?

925
01:21:15.292 --> 01:21:17.375
<font color="#ffff33">Oh!</font>


926
01:21:18.459 --> 01:21:24.917
<font color="#ffff33">- Oh. - Uncouple the trailer. We got a wellhead to deliver.</font>
Dételle la remorque. On a une livraison à faire.

927
01:21:31.459 --> 01:21:33.667
<font color="#ffff33">Oh. geez.</font>
Bon sang.

928
01:21:33.709 --> 01:21:36.625
<font color="#ffff33">It's not as bad as it looks.</font>
C'est moins méchant que ça en a l'air.

929
01:21:38.375 --> 01:21:40.480
<font color="#ffff33">It's. uh...</font>


930
01:21:40.500 --> 01:21:43.855
<font color="#ffff33">It looks pretty bad. kid.</font>
C'est assez vilain. petite.

931
01:21:43.875 --> 01:21:45.980
<font color="#ffff33">-Just be fast about it. -Uh...</font>
Vas-y d'un coup sec.

932
01:21:46.000 --> 01:21:47.730
<font color="#ffff33">Like pulling out a wisdom tooth.</font>
Comme pour une dent.

933
01:21:47.750 --> 01:21:50.813
<font color="#ffff33">A wisdom tooth? Do I-- Do I look like a dentist?</font>
Une dent ? J'ai une tête de dentiste ?

934
01:21:50.833 --> 01:21:53.292
<font color="#ffff33">Aah!</font>


935
01:21:53.459 --> 01:21:55.105
<font color="#ffff33">Good girl. Good girl.</font>
C'est bien.

936
01:21:55.125 --> 01:21:57.042
<font color="#ffff33">Breathe. Breathe.</font>
Respire.

937
01:21:57.458 --> 01:22:00.439
<font color="#ffff33">That's it. Good girl. Good girl.</font>
Voilà. C'est bien.

938
01:22:00.459 --> 01:22:03.250
<font color="#ffff33">Gurty. come and help me!</font>
Gurty ! Viens m'aider.

939
01:22:04.042 --> 01:22:07.189
<font color="#ffff33">Good girl. Good girl.</font>
C'est bien.

940
01:22:07.209 --> 01:22:09.167
<font color="#ffff33">Come on.</font>
Viens.

941
01:22:15.917 --> 01:22:17.439
<font color="#ffff33">Hang tight.</font>
Tiens bon.

942
01:22:17.459 --> 01:22:20.605
<font color="#ffff33">Gurty and I are going to haul your trailer off the cliff.</font>
On va remettre ta remorque sur la route.

943
01:22:20.625 --> 01:22:24.147
<font color="#ffff33">hook up and head to that mine.</font>
l'atteler et l'amener à la mine.

944
01:22:24.167 --> 01:22:26.647
<font color="#ffff33">We still got 45 minutes.</font>
Il nous reste 45 minutes.

945
01:22:26.667 --> 01:22:28.792
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah.</font>


946
01:22:57.542 --> 01:22:59.272
<font color="#ffff33">Sir? Mine Safety down in Winnipeg wants René's laptops.</font>
Monsieur. La sécurité minière

947
01:22:59.292 --> 01:23:01.605
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
veut les ordinateurs de René.

948
01:23:01.625 --> 01:23:05.813
<font color="#ffff33">Fred. Mine Safety gets the laptops when I say they get the laptops. all right?</font>
La sécurité minière va devoir attendre. compris ?

949
01:23:05.833 --> 01:23:07.772
<font color="#ffff33">We got a goddamn CEO to worry about.</font>
On doit déjà gérer le PDG.

950
01:23:07.792 --> 01:23:12.750
<font color="#ffff33">Yeah. well. you can tell him yourself. He'll be here in an hour.</font>
Ça tombe bien. il est en route.

951
01:23:14.084 --> 01:23:18.647
<font color="#ffff33">There is nothing in those e-mails that implicates us.</font>
Il n'y a rien dans ces mails qui nous incrimine.

952
01:23:18.667 --> 01:23:21.688
<font color="#ffff33">Everything was cash. so there's no paper trail.</font>
On payait en cash. il n'y a aucune trace.

953
01:23:21.708 --> 01:23:29.167
<font color="#ffff33">To the authorities. this just looks like another tragic mining accident.</font>
Les autorités concluront à un tragique accident de mine.

954
01:23:30.209 --> 01:23:31.772
<font color="#ffff33">Right in the morning. we open Tunnel 6.</font>
Demain matin.

955
01:23:31.792 --> 01:23:33.647
<font color="#ffff33"></font>
on ouvre le tunnel 6.

956
01:23:33.667 --> 01:23:35.647
<font color="#ffff33">We remove the bodies.</font>
on sort les corps.

957
01:23:35.667 --> 01:23:38.480
<font color="#ffff33">We let the public hold their ritual funerals.</font>
on laisse les familles vaquer à leurs rites funéraires.

958
01:23:38.500 --> 01:23:43.439
<font color="#ffff33">We weather the obligatory "occupational hazard" debate.</font>
on se plie à l'inévitable débat sur les risques du métier...

959
01:23:43.459 --> 01:23:45.875
<font color="#ffff33">And we open back up.</font>
et on reprend l'exploitation.

960
01:23:46.000 --> 01:23:48.375
<font color="#ffff33">Business as usual.</font>
Les affaires continuent.

961
01:23:53.292 --> 01:23:57.584
<font color="#ffff33">Come on. Varnay. answer the goddamn phone.</font>
Répondez. Varnay. bon Dieu.

962
01:24:46.125 --> 01:24:47.814
<font color="#ffff33">Look. Gurty. we did it.</font>
Regarde. on a réussi.

963
01:24:47.834 --> 01:24:49.917
<font color="#ffff33">We did it!</font>
